tagline: A central page for all of my GitHub stuff!
body:
### Welcome to my GitHub page!
This is my GitHub page. You can stare at my various Java projects here (and laugh at my mistakes, if you don't want to help me fix them) and see the source code for them.

### BukkitPluginMD
I wrote a simple Bukkit plugin before the whole DMCA thing happened.  
You can see the source code [here](BukkitPluginMD) in case you were interested.

### WhiteCraft
WhiteCraft is a mod about... umm... I haven't got that far yet. You can grind stuff up and refuel stuff, though.  
The source code is available [here](WhiteCraft).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
